    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <div>GiiMote is an extension package for <a href="http://www.yoyogames.com/" target="_blank">Game Maker</a> and <a href="http://www.mathworks.com/" target="_blank">MATLAB</a> which adds support for the Wii Remote.</div>
    <div>GiiMote is a wrapper for Brian Peek's managed library for Nintendo's Wii Remote, "WiimoteLib" which can be found at <a href="http://www.codeplex.com/WiimoteLib" target="_blank">http://www.codeplex.com/WiimoteLib</a>. WiimoteLib is licensed under the Ms-PL.</div>
